verbose_text: Data from this study showed that the addition with either 10,000 ~ 200,000-fold diluted proprietary antioxidant supplement or 1 ~ 20 muM homemade antioxidant cocktail in the culture medium did not affect the growth and " stemness " of iPS cells by 2 months follow-up, although the additions with antioxidants significantly decreased ROS levels in iPS cells.
